Module imagingbook.parboiled.java

module imagingbook.parboiled.java
This is a modularized version of the parboiled PEG parser Java/Scala implementation originally developed by Mathias Doenitz, refactored from Version 1.4.1 (Jan. 2023). See https://github.com/sirthias/parboiled for the original project.
